My anger will burn against them on that day;
 I will abandon them and hide my face from them so that they will become easy prey.
 Many troubles and afflictions will come to them. On that day they will say, ‘Haven’t these troubles come to us because our God is no longer with us?’

19:
Therefore write down this song
 for yourselves and teach it to the Israelites; have them sing it,
 so that this song may be a witness for me against the Israelites.

